{"tid":2267723,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泰民回歸倒數一週⋯⋯將與師妹 Wendy 合作！","createTime":"2020-11-02T09:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T00:44:25.000Z","uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"794b73d754dcf0d19e82aae63b79213b7365b287","tid":2267723,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_21dc9313bfeeec390f6347624eccc565/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-02/131339-882940.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_21dc9313bfeeec390f6347624eccc565%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-02%2F131339-882940.png&h=fae8276a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連日來釋出新專輯概念照的 SHINee 泰民，又加碼公開了好消息。很好奇他和 Wendy 的合作會走什麼路線呢！<br />\n<br />\nSM Entertainment 今天（2 日）上午透露泰民這次為正規三輯〈Never Gonna Dance Again: Act 2〉收錄的 &ldquo;Heaven&rdquo;、「想擁抱你」(Think of You) 和 &ldquo;Pansy&rdquo; 三首歌參與了作詞工作；除此之外，Red Velvet 的 Wendy 還為他跨刀獻聲合作 &ldquo;Be Your Enemy&rdquo; 一曲，消息一出立刻掀起各國粉絲的熱烈迴響。<br />\n<br />\n泰民首先在今年 9 月時推出久違的正規專輯〈Never Gonna Dance Again: Act 1〉，接下來則準備以彷彿電影續集的 Act 2，為涵蓋豐富情節與故事的一系列音樂作畫下句點。<br />\n<br />\n〈Never Gonna Dance Again: Act 2〉包含主打歌「IDEA:理想」和 &ldquo;Be Your Enemy&rdquo; 在內共收錄 9 首新歌，並將於韓國時間 11 月 9 日傍晚 6 點正式發行。在那之前，就先來回味泰民上次的作品吧！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：SM Entertainment）"},{"pid":"a8fb4efc5aa35f362efe73aa2cea98126d2f429b","tid":2267723,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:38:15.000Z","msg":"回歸師"},{"pid":"0e9af5cb35cd5b08ba8b1d653305d02690d6239f","tid":2267723,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42937b3bb15f2c95b243473e80053aed518db43","tid":2267723,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re